            Whether you're planning a weekend getaway or a month-long adventure, we have the perfect 
            accommodation waiting for you.
        </div>
        
        <a href="/listings" class="cta-button">
            Explore Listings üöÄ
        </a>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">üåü</div>
